@startuml sq_edt01_select_strategy
' ============================================================
' Title:     EDT-01 — SELECT Edit Strategy
' Boundary:  nasim code agent CLI
' Purpose:   Choose optimal edit format for the target model
' Milestone: v1.0
' Version:   1.0.0
' Source:    docs/audit/audit.2026.06.20.deep.domain.audit.md
' Review:    —
' ============================================================

actor "Developer" as user

box "Agent Layer" #E3F2FD
  participant "AgentOrchestrator" as agent
end box
box "Edit Layer" #FFF3E0
  participant "EditStrategySelector" as selector
  participant "EditFormat" as format
end box
box "Provider Layer" #E3F2FD
  participant "Provider" as provider
end box
box "Config Layer" #E8F5E9
  participant "Config" as config
end box

note over user, config
  Scope:
    - edt01 SELECT Strategy — choose optimal edit format for model

  Preconditions:
    - Agent has identified a file to edit
    - Config loaded with supported edit formats

  Contexts:
    - Called before EDT-02 (Apply Edit)
    - Entry point for the edit subsystem

  Excludes:
    - Edit execution (handled by EDT-02)
    - Edit validation (handled by EDT-03)

  Rollback:
    - No valid strategy → return error, suggest manual edit

  Design:
    - EditStrategySelector evaluates model capabilities vs edit requirements
    - Supported formats: SEARCH_REPLACE, UNIFIED_DIFF, FULL_REWRITE, INSERT_LINE
    - Strategy selected based on: model support, diff size, file type
    - Large diffs (>50 lines) prefer FULL_REWRITE
    - Small surgical edits prefer SEARCH_REPLACE

  Returns:
    - Success: EditStrategy with format and parameters
    - Failure: Error with recommendation
end note

== edt01 SELECT Strategy ==

agent -> selector : SELECT_STRATEGY(file_path, edit_description, model_id)
activate selector

selector -> config : get_supported_formats(model_id)
activate config
config --> selector : supported_formats[]
deactivate config

selector -> selector : estimate_diff_size(edit_description)

alt diff_size <= 5 lines
    selector -> format : CREATE_SEARCH_REPLACE(file_path, edit_description)
    activate format
    format --> selector : SearchReplaceEdit
    deactivate format
else diff_size <= 50 lines
    selector -> format : CREATE_UNIFIED_DIFF(file_path, edit_description)
    activate format
    format --> selector : UnifiedDiffEdit
    deactivate format
else diff_size > 50 lines
    selector -> format : CREATE_FULL_REWRITE(file_path, edit_description)
    activate format
    format --> selector : FullRewriteEdit
    deactivate format
end

selector -> selector : validate_format_compatibility(strategy, model_id)

selector --> agent : EditStrategy(format, parameters, confidence)
deactivate selector

note over user, config
  Flow:
    - AgentOrchestrator → EditStrategySelector → Config + EditFormat → EditStrategy

  State:
    - IDLE → EVALUATING → SELECTING → VALIDATING → READY

  Failure:
    - No compatible format → error + manual suggestion

  Success:
    - EditStrategy with chosen format and parameters

  Key invariants:
    - Selected format always supported by target model
    - Confidence score reflects strategy reliability
    - Fallback chain: SEARCH_REPLACE → UNIFIED_DIFF → FULL_REWRITE
end note

@enduml
